{"tid":1968738,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】美華特迪士尼世界 4.3 萬員工無薪休假一年","createTime":"2020-04-12T02:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T04:12:42.000Z","uid":158735,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ddaff5f2945213eccae39221ae602f13a7509d6c","tid":1968738,"uid":158735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%AF%E7%89%B9%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-4-3-%E8%90%AC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E4%BC%91%E5%81%87%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-4-3-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2581%2587%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2FiPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=e128825f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-4-3-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2581%2587%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&h=bf06c43b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%AF%E7%89%B9%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-4-3-%E8%90%AC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E4%BC%91%E5%81%87%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4/</a><br />\n<br />\n立場報道2020/4/12 &mdash; 9:48<br />\n美國華特迪士尼世界推出一年無薪休假計劃，於一星期內，停止向 4.3 萬名僱員支付薪水，但保留福利，是武漢肺炎疫症爆發以來，最大規劃的無薪假計劃。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼工會表示，員工在休假期間仍獲得醫療、牙齒等福利及保險，比起其他公司的休假甚至裁員計劃，已經算是較大保障。<br />\n<br />\n一年休假計劃於 4 月 19 日 實施，員工的職級、工資水平會凍結不變。期間有 200 名員工會繼續工作，以維持必須的工作。<br />\n<br />\n有 7.7 萬名員工的迪士尼世界是全美最大僱員群組。早前，多個代表護衛員、音樂演奏家、遊樂場設施操作員等工會已先後與資方達成類似協議。"},{"pid":"4de0ae382c8fb85407eaa2a8ad71010a78297177","tid":1968738,"uid":344567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"用開和路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446deb63e0dfe9d81be9b982fd086bab62e1434b","tid":1968738,"uid":158735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4de0ae382c8fb85407eaa2a8ad71010a78297177","tid":1968738,"uid":344567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"用開和路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱想講<br />\n華特唔係普通話譯名?"},{"pid":"7c332730861d12a5edb396fcbe4206d54e3463a9","tid":1968738,"uid":101616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:13:22.000Z","msg":"香港迪迪尼駛唔駛跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0624f43964872f07cfac77c9fbe8c5b1c14e5ee","tid":1968738,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"一年唔出糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240f40a2c572a63dfb33ebf0dabd388d9cc116ad","tid":1968738,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446deb63e0dfe9d81be9b982fd086bab62e1434b","tid":1968738,"uid":158735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quot